# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# EWA Backend – Environment Variables Template
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to .env (never commit .env to git)
# supply real values in Azure DevOps variable groups
# or Oracle VM secrets manager.

# ── Spring DataSource (Neon PostgreSQL) ──────────────
SPRING_DATASOURCE_URL=jdbc:postgresql://<host>/<db>?sslmode=require&channel_binding=require
SPRING_DATASOURCE_USERNAME=<neon_user>
SPRING_DATASOURCE_PASSWORD=<neon_password>

# ── JWT ──────────────────────────────────────────────
JWT_SECRET=<64-character-hex-secret>
JWT_EXPIRATION=86400000

# ── Spring Profiles ───────────────────────────────────
SPRING_PROFILES_ACTIVE=prod

# ── JPA / Hibernate ──────────────────────────────────
# Use 'validate' or 'none' in production; 'update' only for initial deploy
SPRING_JPA_HIBERNATE_DDL_AUTO=update
